== Thinking Sphinx on Windows Example App

Thinking sphinx on windows can be a pain. 

Follow this guide http://www.espace.com.eg/blog/2009/03/23/thinking-sphinx-on-windows/

And then delete log/searchd.development.pid , run rake ts:rebuild and on you go.

The following is an example app showing listings, pagination and sorting, the main use of this should be to see the setup of how it works on windows though.